<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3366698>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Details of dorsal pholidosis at mid-body of (A) Cnemaspis koynaensis sp. nov., holotype, NCBS-BH685, (C) Cnemaspis amba sp. nov., holotype, NCBS-BH690 and details of ventral scales at mid-body, (B) Cnemaspis koynaensis sp. nov., holotype, NCBS-BH685, and (D) Cnemaspis amba sp. nov., holotype, NCBS-BH690. Scale bars 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3366698/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3366692>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Cnemaspis koynaensis sp. nov. (holotype, NCBS-BH685): (A) dorsal view of head, (B) ventral view of head, (C) lateral view of head, (D) view of cloacal region showing femoral pores, (E) ventral view of right manus, and (F) ventral view of right pes. Scale bars 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3366692/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3366690>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Cnemaspis koynaensis sp. nov. (holotype, NCBS-BH685): (A) dorsal view of body, (B) ventral view of body, (C) dorsal view of tail, and (D) ventral view of tail. Scale bars 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3366690/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3366696>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Cnemaspis koynaensis sp. nov. in life. (A) male, holotype, NCBS-BH685, (B) an uncollected juvenile, and (C) male, paratype, NCBS-BH685." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3366696/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3366708>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Habitat photos of, (A) Cnemaspis koynaensis sp. nov., near Dhanagarwada, Humbarli village, Koyna, Satara District, Maharashtra and (B) Cnemaspis amba sp. nov. near Kokan Darshan Point, Manoli village, near Amba, Kolhapur District, Maharashtra, respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3366708/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

